Charles Lamy https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Charles_Lamy 0 For the 19th-century politician, see Charles Lamy (New York).Charles Lamy (28 August 1857 – 15 June 1940) was a French actor. He was often cast to play aristocratic characters.Lamy was born in Lyon, France and died in Orléans in 1940. For the_19th-century_politician , see Charles_Lamy ( New_York ) .
